        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "How a folder opens its base. 'Plain click' opens on a normal click; 'Modifier + click' requires holding the modifier key.",
          "target": "文件夹如何打开其基础。'普通点击'在正常点击时打开；'修饰键 + 点击'需要按住修饰键。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Modifier used for the 'Modifier + click' trigger and for creating a base on click.",
          "target": "用于'修饰键 + 点击'触发器和点击创建基础的修饰键。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "When a folder has no base, a modifier + click creates one from the default template and opens it.",
          "target": "当文件夹没有基础时，按住修饰键并点击会从默认模板创建一个并打开它。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "When you create a new folder, generate its base from the template automatically (it isn't opened). Respects the folder filter.",
          "target": "创建新文件夹时，自动从模板生成其基础（不会打开它）。遵循文件夹过滤器。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Only auto-create when the new folder already holds at least this many notes. 0 creates a base for every new folder.",
          "target": "仅当新文件夹已包含至少此数量的笔记时才自动创建。0 表示为每个新文件夹创建基础。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "When a plain click opens a base, also expand/collapse the folder as usual. If off, the folder stays put.",
          "target": "当普通点击打开基础时，也照常展开/折叠文件夹。如果关闭，文件夹保持原状。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Where a base opens when triggered. 'Reuse existing tab' focuses an already-open tab if there is one. Middle-clicking a folder always opens in a new tab.",
          "target": "触发时基础在哪里打开。'重用现有标签页'会聚焦已打开的标签页（如果存在）。中键点击文件夹总是在新标签页中打开。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
